  "title": "Service Desk Analyst at Gombak, Up to $3,600 (depends on experience) (12hr Shift)",
  "description": "<p><strong>- 2 years contract (renewable & convertible)</strong></p><p><strong>- Up to $3,600 (depends on experience)</strong></p><p><strong>- Monday to Friday: 12 hrs Shift, 9pm-9am</strong></p><p><strong>- Gombak</strong><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>We are looking for an Assistant Engineer to be an essential member of a 24/7 Service Desk to ensure high availability of our customer’s enterprise IT services and to restore normal IT service to affected users as quickly as possible.</p><ul><li>Monitor enterprise IT networks and server systems</li><li>Act as a single point of contact to customers/users, resolver groups, third party service providers and other departments</li><li>Respond to hotline calls and e-mails within agreed timescales</li><li>Take ownership of incidents/service requests reported by users, track the incidents/service requests, to ensure closure within agreed timescales</li><li>Maintain documentation and comprehensive records of issues and problems</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Period:</strong></p><ul><li>2 years contract (renewable & convertible)</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Location:</strong></p><ul><li>Gombak</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li>Monday to Friday: 12 hrs Shift, 9pm-9am</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong></p><ul><li>Up to $3,600 (depends on experience)</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum higher NITEC in Information Technology or equivalent. Open to fresh candidates with relevant internship experience.</p></li><li>1 to 2 years of working experience.</li><li>Strong teamwork and communication skills</li><li>Excellent customer service skills</li><li>Prior experience in Network Operations Centre (NOC) environment preferred</li><li>Able to work 12-hour Rotating Day and Night shift working including weekends and Public Holidays</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly email your detailed resume (MS Word format is preferred):</p><p><strong>azmin@successhrc.com.sg (Reg No:</strong> <strong>R25129300)</strong><br /></p><p>Please ensure that applications sent through email are <strong>no bigger than 1Mb</strong>.</p><p>We thank all applicants for your interest but regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates would be notified.<br /></p><p><strong>Success Resource Centre Pte Ltd</strong> (EA License Number: <strong>04C3201</strong>)</p><p>160 Robinson Road, #13-07/08/09 SBF Center, Singapore 068914<br />T: 6337 3183 | W: <a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.successhrc.com.sg</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.successhrc.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
